name: PEACE Beach Photo Inspirational Domino Pendant
description:
This is an extremely unique pendant - I made it from start to finish!

We went to Jericho Beach just before New Year's and I took some photos and played with them in photo editing software.  Then I made it into this upcycled domino pendant!

This one features the word "Peace".  Of course it would not be complete without my signature sparkly crystal in the corner. Inspirational and sweet!

This pendant will come with a sterling silver plated chain - 16" long with an extender to 18" and in a cute little organza gift bag.

name: Live Laugh Love Domino Pendant
description:
This super cute pendant is made from an upcycled domino game piece!  I also created the image using my graphic design skills!

It features the words"Live, Laugh, Love" and a big black heart on a tie-die background.  Inspirational and sweet!

This pendant comes with a sterling silver plated chain - 16" long with an extender to 18" and will come in a cute organza bag.
